programme.title: Catch Me if You Claus
programme.desc: Avery Quinns shot at anchoring news clashes with a Santa-suited intruder, Chris, who insists hes Santas son on a first Christmas mission. They unravel a career-making story together.

programme.title: Following Yonder Star
programme.desc: A former television star waits out a scandal in Vermont. She becomes close with the innkeeper and his daughter while she helps him direct the local Christmas pageant.

programme.title: Christmas Wishes and Mistletoe Kisses
programme.desc: Weeks before Christmas, an interior designer is hired to decorate the estate of a wealthy businessman.

programme.title: Miracle in Bethlehem, PA
programme.desc: A single woman with a newly adopted baby gets stuck in Bethlehem, Pa.; with no room at the inn, shes forced to stay with a stranger who turns out to be the miracle she has needed.

programme.title: A Timeless Christmas
programme.desc: A man travels from 1903 to 2020, where he meets a tour guide at his historic mansion and gets to experience a 21st century Christmas.

programme.title: The Christmas House
programme.desc: Working through some difficult decisions, a mother and father summon their two grown sons home for the holidays.

programme.title: The Christmas House 2: Deck Those Halls
programme.desc: Excited for a calm Christmas, Mike Mitchell unexpectedly gets roped into a Christmas house-decorating reality TV show against his brother.

programme.title: Hollywood on Set
programme.desc: Features behind-the-scenes footage from movie sets and discussions with the cast and crew about the details of each film.

programme.title: Moms Christmas Boyfriend
programme.desc: A precocious 10-year-old girl makes a Christmas wish for her adoptive mother to find true love.

programme.title: The Most Colorful Time of the Year
programme.desc: A colorblind elementary school teacher meets an optometrist who helps bring color into his life in time for the holidays.

programme.title: Haul Out the Holly: Lit Up
programme.desc: Emily and Jared are looking forward to celebrating the holidays together again, this time as a couple. Theyre also ready to work with members of the community to make this years Christmas festivities the best yet.

programme.title: Christmas at the Plaza
programme.desc: When historian Jessica is hired to create the Plazas Christmas display, she finds more than facts while teaming up with handsome decorator Nick to bring the display to life.

programme.title: Where Are You, Christmas?
